frontend_notes.q3_dynamic_filtering: Use valid_q3_options to show only education levels that have matching occupations for the selected Q1+Q2 path.
frontend_notes.q4_option_count: 4 of 18 Q4 branches have 8-9 options. Consider a scrollable list or two-column layout for these. Revisit during design/UAT phase.
frontend_notes.small_leaves: 8 leaves have 1-2 occupations (niche roles). Render gracefully — the user simply sees a short list.
frontend_notes.empty_path_handling: 18 Q1+Q2+Q3 combos have no occupations. The valid_q3_options map prevents users from reaching these by filtering Q3 choices dynamically.
